{"tid":2073120,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"杜汶澤寸警察着制服做衰嘢","createTime":"2020-06-21T05:43:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T05:45:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c80ac248306497c593f92b6583e92fd8ec8c4eea","tid":2073120,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T05:43:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200621/HVR2QFTP5PGV5JEGG5LM3S7D7Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200621%2FHVR2QFTP5PGV5JEGG5LM3S7D7Q%2F&d=CgUtGs1XjGBKDnLe79D2Ywp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=a688a90a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200621%2FHVR2QFTP5PGV5JEGG5LM3S7D7Q%2F&h=cdc4ea61\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200621/HVR2QFTP5PGV5JEGG5LM3S7D7Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n杜汶澤寸警察着制服做衰嘢<br />\n<br />\n杜汶澤自去年逆權運動開始，不斷撐手足鬧爆政府無能高官，。。。。教育局指學生不應穿校服參加政治活動，聲稱會令人誤會代表全校師生立場，並指會聯絡有關學校跟進。<br />\n<br />\n杜汶澤前晚在fb揶揄教育局打壓學生的公民權是多此一舉，並留言寸爆黑警：「教育局話學生着校服參加校外政治活動，會令人誤會係代表全校師生立場。哦，原來uniform係咁powerful，咁一個着住警察制服嘅人做埋啲衰嘢，就代表整個警隊30,000人都係黑警？係咪咁意思？」<br />\n<br />\n撰文：祖李<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RADGBRSUSX7EOMW3EJRNB2WUWY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRADGBRSUSX7EOMW3EJRNB2WUWY.jpg&h=535f742c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n杜汶澤借警察制服，揶揄教育局指學生不應穿校服參加政治活動。資料圖片<br />\n杜汶澤借警察制服，揶揄教育局指學生不應穿校服參加政治活動。資料圖片"},{"pid":"a4ae1769671eff76350eeadf649a7a5ac8db3bf2","tid":2073120,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T05:44:50.000Z","msg":"以局長嘅邏輯嚟講：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係</span></span>"},{"pid":"fe1734105bac8be68f6dd326a1bfcf807359e44e","tid":2073120,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T05:45:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">死黑警</span></span>"}]}